  "title": "Videographer / Content Producer",
  "description": "<ul><li><em><strong>Partner of MNCs</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Basic from $4,000 to $5,000 + Bonus</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Monday – Friday, 9:30am – 6:30pm</strong></em></li><li><em><strong>Location: Chinatown</strong></em></li></ul><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li>Collaborate closely with the Content and Social Media teams to conceptualise and execute video campaigns</li><li>Provide early-stage input during ideation to help assess feasibility, resource needs, and production timelines</li><li>Conduct video shoots — whether structured or spontaneous — tailored for short-form content</li><li>Edit and assemble raw footage into compelling, platform-optimised video assets with minimal supervision</li><li>Manage the entire post-production workflow from first cut to final delivery</li><li>Maintain high creative standards under tight deadlines</li><li>Identify and adopt emerging trends in social video formats and editing techniques</li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li>Proven experience as a shooter-editor, particularly in creating content for TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube Shorts</li><li>Strong familiarity with local pop culture, online trends, and Singaporean social context (slang, humour, and pacing)</li><li>Ability to deliver high-quality work independently and respond positively to feedback</li><li>A proactive, problem-solving mindset with the ability to thrive in fast-paced production cycles</li><li>A portfolio demonstrating experience in short-form video production and editing is required</li></ul><p><em><strong>For consideration, kindly submit your CV by clicking “APPLY NOW”</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>**Only shortlisted candidates would be notified**</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752</strong></em></p><p><em><strong>EA. Registration No.: R24123733 | Chen Yit Keat</strong></em></p><p></p>",
